snippet.title: Abigail - Roses With Thorns (Character Trailer) | Dislyte
snippet.description:
Strong as the beautiful rose that blooms alone in the snowfields, she won't allow the words of other people to sway her decisions.
She is Abigail, the Queen of Roses from the snowfields.
